{"MANHANDLE":[{"def":"To move, or manage, by human force without mechanical aid; as, to manhandle a cannon.","pos":""},{"def":"To handle roughly; as, the captive was manhandled.","pos":""}],"MANHES PROCESS":[{"def":"A process by which copper matte is treated by passing through it a blast of air, to oxidize and remove sulphur.","pos":""}],"MANHOLE":[{"def":"A hole through which a man may descend or creep into a drain, sewer, steam boiler, parts of machinery, etc.","pos":""}],"MANHOOD":[{"def":"The state of being man as a human being, or man as distinguished from a child or a woman.","pos":""},{"def":"Manly quality; courage; bravery; resolution.","pos":""}]}